<subSubSection id="C30E65693F766D43FF53FD74FE52FC34" pageId="7" pageNumber="366" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BAB36E23F766D43FF53FD74FE52FC34" blockId="7.[151,764,748,1013]" pageId="7" pageNumber="366">
This species belongs to the 
<taxonomicName id="4C144D613F766D43FDEFFD74FD85FCC7" baseAuthorityName="Sundevall" baseAuthorityYear="1846" box="[513,581,748,774]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="366" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="caffer">
<emphasis id="B960EAF03F766D43FDEFFD74FD85FCC7" box="[513,581,748,774]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="366">caffer</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
/ 
<taxonomicName id="4C144D613F766D43FDA0FD74FD4FFCC7" baseAuthorityName="Noack" baseAuthorityYear="1893" box="[590,655,748,774]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="366" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ruber">
<emphasis id="B960EAF03F766D43FDA0FD74FD4FFCC7" box="[590,655,748,774]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="366">ruber</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex and has yet to be named, but has been placed in the lineage E1 (Vallo 
<emphasis id="B960EAF03F766D43FE89FCA8FE5AFC8B" box="[359,410,816,842]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="366">et al</emphasis>
., 2008). Morphologically, it is indistinguishable from the previous species, but differs in echolocation call (Monadjem 
<emphasis id="B960EAF03F766D43FDBDFCEDFD49FC4E" box="[595,649,885,911]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="366">et al</emphasis>
., 2013 
<emphasis id="B960EAF03F766D43FD32FCEDFD2BFC4E" box="[732,747,885,911]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="366">b</emphasis>
). This species has been recorded roosting widely, and in large numbers, in old mine adits on the Liberian side of the mountain.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
